      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/troubled-pennsylvania-hospital-chain-preps-1-billion-debt-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的宾夕法尼亚州医院连锁机构 Tower Health 计划交换现有债务并筹集更多资金，以实现扭亏为盈。]]></description>
